export enum FlexBoxWrap { /** * All will stay on one line.
* Note: Corresponds to `nowrap`. */ NoWrap = 'NoWrap', /** * Items will wrap onto multiple lines. (top to bottom)
* Note: Corresponds to `wrap`. */ Wrap = 'Wrap', /** * Items will wrap onto multiple lines. (bottom to top)
* Note: Corresponds to `wrap-reverse`. */ WrapReverse = 'WrapReverse' }
